\newlabel{tab:main}{{2}{5}{In-distribution accuracy (\%, multi-seed averages). Standard GRPO (lr=5e-7) fails in every domain. With properly tuned learning rate, GRPO matches or exceeds SFT in all five domains. On-policy self-distillation (OPD), evaluated separately on the full test set, produces no meaningful improvement over base in the three domains tested (Appendix~\ref {sec:opd_results}).\relax }{table.caption.2}{}}
