\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces GRPO reward trajectories on Medicine at different learning rates. At standard lr=5e-7 (gray), reward remains trapped near initialization, the mode-seeking trap. Higher learning rates progressively escape this trap, with lr=2e-5 (rose) achieving reward 0.94 and translating to +7.4\% test accuracy. Translucent band shows multi-seed variance.\relax }}{6}{figure.caption.5}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:reward_traj}{{2}{6}{GRPO reward trajectories on Medicine at different learning rates. At standard lr=5e-7 (gray), reward remains trapped near initialization, the mode-seeking trap. Higher learning rates progressively escape this trap, with lr=2e-5 (rose) achieving reward 0.94 and translating to +7.4\% test accuracy. Translucent band shows multi-seed variance.\relax }{figure.caption.5}{}}
